  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Most nights in the country, George waited up for an important call.",
      "zh": "在鄉下的大多數晚上，喬治都會等著一通重要的電話。",
      "ja": "田舎のほとんどの夜、ジョージは重要な電話を待っていました。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Calling George.",
      "zh": "打給喬治。",
      "ja": "ジョージに電話しています。",
      "time": "00:00:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is George?",
      "zh": "喬治在做什麼？",
      "ja": "ジョージは何をしているの？",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have the most amazing, exciting thing to tell you.",
      "zh": "我有件非常驚人又令人興奮的事要告訴你。",
      "ja": "とても素晴らしくてワクワクすることを話したいんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can you come over?",
      "zh": "你能過來嗎？",
      "ja": "来られる？",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Er...",
      "zh": "呃...",
      "ja": "ええと...",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, right.",
      "zh": "喔，對了。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね。",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're in bed.",
      "zh": "我們正在床上。",
      "ja": "私たちはベッドにいるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, then.",
      "zh": "那好吧。",
      "ja": "じゃあ、そうしよう。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe at the clubhouse tomorrow.",
      "zh": "也許明天在會所見。",
      "ja": "明日クラブハウスで会おうか。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Right away.",
      "zh": "馬上。",
      "ja": "すぐにね。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't forget.",
      "zh": "別忘了。",
      "ja": "忘れないでね。",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye!",
      "zh": "再見！",
      "ja": "バイバイ！",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Aha!",
      "zh": "啊哈！",
      "ja": "あは！",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Haha!",
      "zh": "哈哈！",
      "ja": "はは！",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The next morning, George raced to the clubhouse.",
      "zh": "隔天早上，喬治急忙跑向會所。",
      "ja": "翌朝、ジョージはクラブハウスへ急いで向かいました。",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah!",
      "zh": "啊！",
      "ja": "ああ！",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, hey!",
      "zh": "嘿，嘿！",
      "ja": "やあ、やあ！",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi, George.",
      "zh": "嗨，喬治。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、ジョージ。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you ready to hear this?",
      "zh": "你準備好聽這個了嗎？",
      "ja": "これを聞く準備はできた？",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you ready?",
      "zh": "你準備好了嗎？",
      "ja": "準備はいい？",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's kind of unbelievable.",
      "zh": "這有點難以置信。",
      "ja": "ちょっと信じられないことなんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
