      "ja": "幼稚園は大きくなったら行くところだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And you need to learn stuff like how to write your name",
      "zh": "你需要學習像是怎麼寫你的名字",
      "ja": "そして名前の書き方などを学ぶんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "in 8 plus 2.",
      "zh": "還有8加2。",
      "ja": "8足す2とかね。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah!",
      "zh": "啊！",
      "ja": "ああ！",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I want you to come with me to get all my school tools.",
      "zh": "我想讓你跟我一起去買所有學校用品。",
      "ja": "そして僕と一緒に学校の道具を全部揃えに行こう。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So, can you come?",
      "zh": "所以，你能來嗎？",
      "ja": "だから、来られる？",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh-huh!",
      "zh": "嗯哼！",
      "ja": "うん！",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It was a good thing George went shopping with Ali",
      "zh": "喬治和艾莉一起去購物真是太好了，",
