    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All that morning, George tried to learn the rules of kindergarten.",
      "zh": "整個上午，喬治試著學習幼稚園的規則。",
      "ja": "その朝ずっと、ジョージは幼稚園のルールを学ぼうとしました。",
      "time": "00:06:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here's the castle.",
      "zh": "這是城堡。",
      "ja": "ここが城だ。",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here's the moat.",
      "zh": "這是護城河。",
      "ja": "ここが堀だ。",
      "time": "00:06:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here's where the horses live.",
      "zh": "這是馬兒住的地方。",
      "ja": "ここが馬の住処だ。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa, whoa, whoa!",
