      "role": "student",
      "text": "Kindergarten is harder than it looks.",
      "zh": "幼稚園比看起來還難。",
      "ja": "幼稚園は見た目より難しいんだ。",
      "time": "00:07:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:07:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're a monkey, George.",
      "zh": "你是一隻猴子，喬治。",
      "ja": "君は猿だよ、ジョージ。",
      "time": "00:07:05"
